articles.title: China opens Chang'e 6 return capsule containing samples from moon's far side (video) - Space.com
articles.description: The moon material is being prepared for storage, analysis and research.
articles.content:
China's Chang'e 6 mission return capsule has been transferred to Beijing and opened to access its precious cargo.
